column5: Can you guys give a road condition update on the 502 from the Fort to Dryden? Thanks Alot Terry/IA

Just came back from Red Lake. Used 17 west to 71and then south to Fort Frances. There is alotof road contruction on 502. There are a couplespots on 71 that is under road construction butfound out 71 is by far a better road to travel.
